{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"image-rendering","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/image-rendering","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>« <a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Attribute\" title=\"en/SVG/Attribute\">SVG Attribute reference home</a></p>\n<p><code>image-rendering</code> 属性向浏览器提供了一个提示，即在图片处理时，如何进行速度 vs 质量之间的权衡。<br>\n <br>\n 作为一个显示属性，它也可以在 CSS 样式文件中作为属性而存在，请参考&nbsp; <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/image-rendering\"><code>css image-rendering</code></a> 获取更多的信息</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"使用语境","title":"使用语境","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">类别</th>\n   <td>Presentation attribute</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">值</th>\n   <td><strong>auto</strong> | optimizeSpeed | optimizeQuality | inherit</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">动画效果</th>\n   <td>Yes</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">规范性文件</th>\n   <td><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG11/painting.html#ImageRenderingProperty\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition)</a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"auto\">\n  auto</dt>\n <dd>\n  表示用户代理可以在速度和质量间做适当的权衡，但是质量将比速度更重要一些。</dd>\n <dt id=\"optimizespeed\">\n  optimizeSpeed</dt>\n <dd>\n  表示用户代理应该更注重速度。</dd>\n <dt id=\"optimizequality\">\n  optimizeQuality</dt>\n <dd>\n  表示用户代理应该更注重质量</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"元素","title":"元素","isH3":false,"content":"<p>下面的元素可以能够使用 <code>image-rendering</code> 属性</p>\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/image\"><code>&lt;image&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参考","title":"参考","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/image-rendering\"><code>css image-rendering</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"使用语境","id":"使用语境"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"元素","id":"元素"},{"text":"参考","id":"参考"}],"summary":"« SVG Attribute reference home","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"image-rendering","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/image-rendering","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/image-rendering/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG","title":"SVG"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute","title":"SVG 属性参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/image-rendering","title":"image-rendering"}],"pageTitle":"image-rendering - SVG | MDN","noIndexing":false}}